{"tid":1961134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼城證實 哥迪奧拿82歲母親確診武肺死亡","createTime":"2020-04-06T14:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T14:46:06.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"295aaf8242f5385837274d69556bf28fc9919f03","tid":1961134,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:40:55.000Z","msg":"曼城周一在官方網頁宣佈，領隊哥迪奧拿的母親莎拉（Dolors Sala），在西班牙巴塞隆拿因感染武漢肺炎離世，享年82歲。<br />\n<br />\n曼城表示在這個最令人沮喪的時刻，球會每個人都會向哥迪奧拿及其家人朋友，致以最衷心的同情。<br />\n而同市宿敵曼聯，亦指收到這個可怕的消息而感到難過，並向哥迪奧拿及其家人同樣表示衷心的慰問。"},{"pid":"fff0b2309f546f867820f1f08c246b142831559b","tid":1961134,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200406/GXQV7ILX24OETUIQGDEAJLER7A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200406%2FGXQV7ILX24OETUIQGDEAJLER7A%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le3ljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=cd7c41ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200406%2FGXQV7ILX24OETUIQGDEAJLER7A%2F&h=73da74f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20200406/GXQV7ILX24OETUIQGDEAJLER7A/</a>"},{"pid":"f1864c41e8f33d663e706d9611adb6297adc41ce","tid":1961134,"uid":35507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}